android tethering
USB_ETH_RNDIS
  -> Device Drivers                                                                                                         │  
  │       -> USB support (USB_SUPPORT [=y])                                                                                       │  
  │ (6)     -> USB Gadget Support (USB_GADGET [=n])                                                                               │  
  │           -> USB Gadget Drivers (<choice> [=n])                                                                               │  
  │             -> Ethernet Gadget (with CDC Ethernet support) (USB_ETH [=n])       

http://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/Android_USB_Tethering
